These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
City: colone, hannover, liverpool, boston
1. City:hannover is in an odd position##4
2. City:boston is between City:colone and City:hannover##2
3. City:boston is on the right of City:colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| City   | colone | boston | hannover | liverpool |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: sudoku, collecting, drawing, video-games
1. Hobby:sudoku is on the left of Hobby:video-games##1
2. Hobby:collecting is in an odd position##4
3. Hobby:collecting is on the left or right of Hobby:sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | collecting | sudoku | video-games | drawing |

 #################################
 
