.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, modern, tower
1. House:gothic-revival == House:gothic-revival##1
2. House:tower is on the left or right of House:modern##3
3. House:modern is on the far left or far right##3
4. House:craftsman is in an even position##4
5. House:tower is on the left of House:gothic-revival##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| House   | modern | tower | gothic-revival | craftsman |

